data.description: This home is perfectly situated only 30 min from downtown Austin and ABIA Airport. As you step inside you'll be greeted by a bright open-concept living space that's perfect for hosting family and friends. The living room is perfect for relaxing after a long day. The kitchen has gorgeous granite counter tops and plenty of counter space for preparing meals.  The Primary Suite is a true retreat with a spacious layout, a dedicated sitting area that could be used as an extra office or nursery and a beautiful en-suite bathroom with a nice walk in shower, double vanities, and walk-in closet.  The two additional bedrooms and full bath add for plenty of space for a growing family or guests.  Out back you'll find a fully fenced yard and a nice covered back patio ready for friends. All this only minutes away from shopping!
